extends ../layouts/default

block content
	.panel.panel-default
		.main-title
			p(class='title-header') We are the center of UCSB's neuro-revolution. 
			p We assemble & support research teams to attack the most fundamental problems in brain science. Providing intellectual, technical, and financial resources, we are changing how academic research is done. 
		.secondary-content
			p(class="secondary-header")	Our research is meant to change the future. 
			p	The UCSB Brain Initiative currently sponsors 3 major research teams. Check back soon for the official unveiling.
			p(class="secondary-header")	Our team is all inclusive.
			p	Our team spans from engineering, neuroscience, physics, and computer science to biology, history, literature, communications, & arts.
			p(class="secondary-header")	Learn more about the National Brain Initiative at <a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/BRAIN" target="_blank">whitehouse.gov/BRAIN</a>.
